From d44787d03496ae9f8450ca739f9fbe0990563bc1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thara Gopinath <tgopinath@microsoft.com>
Date: Tue, 30 May 2023 13:13:35 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 15/68] drivers: hv: Add VSM driver to run in VTL1

Add support for basic vsm driver that runs in VTL1. The driver supports
parameter handling for cross VTL communication Saves and restores VTL0
registers on entry into VTL1 and VTL1 registers across vtlcall and
vtlreturn. Register ioctl to enable return to VTL0 when called from the
userspace after boot.

Signed-off-by: Anna Trikalinou <atrikalinou@microsoft.com>
Signed-off-by: Angelina Vu <angelinavu@microsoft.com>
Signed-off-by: Thara Gopinath <tgopinath@microsoft.com>
---
